headline.main: SCENE OF PARLEY LIKE ARMED CAMP; Each Delegate's Villa and Hotel Where Sessions Were Held Under Heavy Guard

lead_paragraph: CAIRO, Egypt, Dec. 1 -- Not since the days of the Ptolemys has Egypt been such a cynosure of attention from the civilized world.
abstract: delegates arrivals, living arrangements, protection, talks progress and attending personnel discussed
